arStrings.szText: Indeed, master Druid. A thief named Darcel snuck in with the knights posing as muscle. Best we handle the matter ourselves, rather than ask the knights for aid.
Merryn is friendly to Druid players.
Aye! A thief named Darcel snuck in with the knights posing as muscle. Took something of mine.
Merryn is suspicious and hesitent to non-Druid players.

A bairn was born healthy a fortnight ago, praise the Glór-an-Fháidha, but the mother is weak. Darcel stole the runic charm I placed to heal her.
Bastard probably just wanted quick coin. He may have condemned both mother and child. Deal with him and bring the charm back.
